RADIUS authentication can be enabled from the ntopng preferences page.

NTOP will request an Access-Request to a radius server.

User is granted if Access-Accept is return, anything else user is
not granted.

If attribute Filter-Id is set to admin user will inherit administrator grant.

Radius authentication parameters are discussed below.

* Radius server
The fqdn / ip of the radius server

* Radius secret
The shared secret between NTOP and radius server.
